### Hadith 1:238

*Narrated Abu Huraira:*

The Prophet said, "A wound which a Muslim receives in Allah's cause will
appear on the Day of Resurrection as it was at the time of infliction;
blood will be flowing from the wound and its color will be that of the
blood but will smell like musk."

